<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(213, 75, 46); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 226);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865076514025962.png" title="1715865076514025962.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 210915.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">为深入学习贯彻习近平总书记关于党纪学习教育的重要讲话和重要指示精神，提高党员的政治觉悟和纪律意识，</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.93em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院学生党支部于2024年4月23日在A10-314党员活动室组织开展党纪学习教育集中学习研讨。本次会议由学生党支部书记熊奕俊主持，党总支专职组织员周婷婷出席，全体学生党员参会。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.93em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865159437093886.png" title="1715865159437093886.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 210926.png" width="907" height="698" style="width: 907px; height: 698px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">本次学习主要分为三个部分进行展开：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1、全体党员逐章逐条学《中国共产党纪律处分条例》（以下简称《条例》）第一章与第二章原文；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2、党员同志集中研讨并分享心得；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">3、学生党支部书记熊奕俊就本次集中学习研讨作总结。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865361402030707.png" title="1715865361402030707.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 210935.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865479655033301.png" title="1715865479655033301.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 210944.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">会议伊始，党总支专职组织员周婷婷和学生党支部书记熊奕俊带头，全体学生党员逐章逐条、原原本本学习《条例》原文内容。本次集中学习了第一章《总体要求和适用范围》以及第二章《违纪与纪律处分内容》。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865746499066473.png" title="1715865746499066473.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 210953.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（党总支专职组织员周婷婷领学）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865788108090326.png" title="1715865788108090326.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211002.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（学生党支部书记熊奕俊领学）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715865981122069059.png" title="1715865981122069059.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211022.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（学生党员原原本本学习）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学习《条例》第一二章原文后，与会党员开展集中研讨，分享学习心得，结合自己的言行进行反思，并就如何改进自身的政治表现和行为进行交流。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党支部书记熊奕俊：<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">新修订的《条例》对全体党员在政治方向、政治立场、政治言论、政治行为方面的纪律规矩进一步做了详细规定。这要求我们在实际工作中，既要坚定理想信念，始终保持正确的政治方向，又要强化政治纪律教育，做到在大是大非面前旗帜鲜明，在风浪考验面前无所畏惧，在各种诱惑面前立场坚定。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866193827055180.png" title="1715866193827055180.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211031.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党员潘茹意：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">守纪律不是空洞抽象的要求，而是具体实在的行为。学习贯彻《条例》决不能“说说”“写写”，必须内化于心、外化于行。自觉将纪律和规矩挺在前面，自重自省自警自励，不断强化党的意识、纪律意识、规矩意识，严格按照党的原则、纪律和规矩办事，把党的纪律真正转化为日常习惯和行动准绳。在今后，我也会自觉对照党的理论和路线方针政策，对照《条例》中政治纪律、组织纪律、廉洁纪律、群众纪律、工作纪律、生活纪律等各项规定，看清哪些事情可以做、哪些事情不该做，将纪律规矩立于心头，融入日常生活的点点滴滴，使其成为一种思维习惯、行为自觉。不断规范和约束自己的言行，努力把纪律、法律转化为高度的自律。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866207567038934.png" title="1715866207567038934.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211040.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党员徐余乐：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在学习过程中，我深感《条例》对于规范党员行为、严肃党内纪律的重要性。它不仅明确了各类违纪行为的处分标准，更是对全体党员敲响了警钟，警示我们要时刻紧绷纪律之弦，做到知敬畏、存戒惧、守底线。作为党员，我们必须将遵守党的纪律内化于心、外化于行，要在实际工作中，以更高的标准严格要求自己，切实履行好党员的责任和义务，永葆共产党人的政治本色。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866217685054117.png" title="1715866217685054117.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211047.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党员汪薇：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学习过程中让我印象较为深刻的是第一章第三条：党章是最根本的党内法规，是管党治党的总规矩。党的纪律是党的各级组织和全体党员必须遵守的行为规则。对我们党员同志来说，必须时刻牢记初心和使命，牢固树立政治意识、大局意识、核心意识、看齐意识，始终坚定道路自信、理论自信、制度自信、文化自信，严格执行和维护党的纪律，自觉接受党的纪律约束，例如大家不要在网上发布不良言论，网络不是法外之地，模范遵守国家法律法规。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866230135087982.png" title="1715866230135087982.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211057.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党员程萱：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学习《条例》第一二章，使我感受到《条例》的每一项规定都是对党员干部行为的约束和指引，是对党的纪律要求的细化和具体化。作为一名党员要时刻保持清醒头脑，增强纪律观念，坚定理想信念，红线不踩、底线不碰，尤其在生活中的小事情上，把住小节，守住底线，“勿以恶小而为之，勿以善小而不为”，在利益诱惑面前始终不忘党的纪律，用更强的党性意识，政治觉悟和纪律要求自己，做一名知纪、畏纪、守纪的党员。&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866239585010444.png" title="1715866239585010444.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211104.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学生党员易玉涵：</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">作为党员，我们要认真学习《条例》内容，时刻铭记纪律挺在前面,党纪面前人人平等，并自觉接受来自各方面的监督，认真开展批评与自我批评。在日常生活中有任何问题或者困惑,都应该及时与老师进行谈话，不能忘记初心，在学习生活中都要发挥好积极的带头作用。做人做事做到忠诚干净担当，一切从人民的利益出发，全心全意为人民服务。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715866253541070086.png" title="1715866253541070086.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 211110.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">最后，学生党支部书记熊奕俊对本次集中学习研讨作总结。他强调党纪学习教育是今年党内政治生活的一件大事，是坚持不懈加强党的纪律建设、纵深推进全面从严治党的重要举措，充分彰显我们党推进自我革命的坚定决心和坚强意志。希望各位党员同志认真落实通知要求，在学习中提升政治站位，切实守住党规党纪底线、不逾越红线、不触碰“高压线”，始终做到忠诚干净担当。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-indent: 30.9999px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">通过本次集中学习研讨《条例》第一第二章，有利于党员同志深入了解党的纪律要求和党员行为规范，增强政治纪律意识和自觉遵守党的规定的能力，同时对提高学生党员的政治素养、增强党性修养、规范行为举止、维护党的形象都具有十分重要的意义。</span></p>